snippet.title: Super Mario Bros: Odyssey (Chapter 1) - World One | Full Gameplay [ No Commentary ]
snippet.description:
Chapter One, World One of Super Mario Bros. Odyssey (Fan Game) by smbmaster99. Download link is in the description.

Super Mario Bros Odyssey Ch.1 is a retelling of the very first Super Mario Bros game, with cutscenes, new sprites, original levels, unlock-able skin-sets and levels, and a few characters and items from future Mario games. "Odyssey" is going to be a series of fan games base on other entries in the Super Mario Bros franchise, with some original ideas.

Hope you enjoy this!
